g.text: Macao SAR China released an estimated 3.12 MtCO2e in 2023 (excl. LULUCF), a change of +3.1 % compared to the previous year.
Per capita GHG emissions were 4.4 tCO2e in 2023. Cumulative CO2 emissions since 1850 were 0.0575 GtCO2, or about 0% of global
emissions to date. Sources: EDGAR v9, GCB 2023, UNFCCC, Grassi et al. 2021
